    intro: "Dubai is the world's most audacious city — a desert metropolis that transformed itself in just 50 years from a small pearl-diving and trading settlement into a global icon of architectural ambition, luxury tourism, and multicultural energy. Home to the world's tallest building, the world's largest mall, and a staggering concentration of record-breaking attractions, Dubai delivers spectacle at every turn. Yet beneath the glass-and-chrome surface lies an authentic Arabic heritage preserved in the labyrinthine lanes of Deira, the wooden abras crossing the historic Creek, and the incense-filled souks that have traded since before the city existed.",
